<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="range-v">range <strong><em>v</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /reɪndʒ/    美 /reɪndʒ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>包括：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The show had a large audience, <strong>ranging from</strong> children <strong>to</strong> grandparents.
这个节目观众很多，从小孩子到爷爷奶奶一辈的都有。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>(价格、水平、温度等) 处于某个范围之内：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The price <strong>ranges between</strong> $25 <strong>and</strong> $400.
价格在25美元到400美元之间。</p></div>

<h4 id="3-wander">3.<strong>漫步; 四处移动 (wander)</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The polar bears range all the way across the Arctic.
北极熊的活动范围遍及整个北极。</p><footer>2019 全国</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>The national park has a large collection of wildlife, <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (range) from butterflies to elephants.  （2017 北京改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. ranging  </p></div>